{"tid":1569392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發現速龍係狗隻入面EQ最低個班","createTime":"2019-09-14T15:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T14:16:53.000Z","uid":58841,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9196e196217a2fc73ea454a8a4b75d46efb7c98c","tid":1569392,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"唔係想洗白 留意左好耐<br />\n速龍真係成隊狗入面EQ特別低一群<br />\n機場特犬更加係低中之低<br />\n3萬狗隻你地知唔知你地百年聲譽俾呢200隻速龍影衰哂<br />\n特別係200隻入面既40隻雞場特犬"},{"pid":"6293ca3b7f63e455b31705372450395754e088fe","tid":1569392,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"【終極核彈】《願榮光》之後－成立海外臨時民主政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566796</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=1fd2149d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"6995f90ebf6833231d032f3cfcbb5b60866040c5","tid":1569392,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:08:35.000Z","msg":"速龍有250隻定200隻唔記得左<br />\n831都係呢班速龍狗衝入去先搞成咁<br />\n記唔記得"},{"pid":"0e3716a9c4fdfa193d37d2227e4adf5d41aac0f3","tid":1569392,"uid":35262,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89eb2775267069bbd9695dd5811694566d6347a5","tid":1569392,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"洗咗腦"},{"pid":"773c1e0d04680c540afc15b9aba982233ff50d4b","tid":1569392,"uid":1452,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"因為佢地可以打完即走<br />\n留低d蘇州屎比condom 仔防暴執<br />\n由佢地企係度比人屌<br />\n所以鍾意點打就點打 點開槍就點開槍"},{"pid":"ec1dc4c46cc10ee7ef1e92829e2f0c98195c806e","tid":1569392,"uid":68896,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:11:24.000Z","msg":"因為朦晒面又無number <br />\n<br />\n打人唔駛負任何責任，所以想打就打，想開槍就開槍，想屌人就屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無形象可言<br />\n<br />\n日後一定要好似烏克蘭防暴咁，解散畜膿"},{"pid":"f38c97f05bc68f3cca565cbdb6c285da43da7ea8","tid":1569392,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:11:36.000Z","msg":"飛狗隊d人   想殺哂你地   平時谷住谷住"},{"pid":"7c8232f37150eeb4328c035272df77e3309780c9","tid":1569392,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"773c1e0d04680c540afc15b9aba982233ff50d4b","tid":1569392,"uid":1452,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"因為佢地可以打完即走<br />\n留低d蘇州屎比condom 仔防暴執<br />\n由佢地企係度比人屌<br />\n所以鍾意點打就點打 點開槍就點開槍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14